{"tid":1715390,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《和理非戰線》最近三罷文宣方向","createTime":"2019-11-13T05:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T08:21:15.000Z","uid":116788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e7f4db0040d1a7353a4ea8ae129abcf5c3eb1a","tid":1715390,"uid":116788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"中大同學奮勇抗暴<br />\n後生仔冒住被捕風險出去塞鐵<br />\n和理非除左罷工之外仲可以做文宣<br />\n<br />\n依家文宣方向唔係呼籲罷工<br />\n要罷既人已經罷緊<br />\n未罷既人就等工會成形吹雞<br />\n依家係要將港豬既怒火轉移去政府身上<br />\n令佢地覺得政府處理唔到依單野<br />\n而且咁多個月以黎既方針係錯<br />\n迫使政府立即採取其它方法解決問題<br />\n<br />\n立即係各大親戚藍屍港豬group帶起風向<br />\n落街痴文宣，Facebook share比廢老"},{"pid":"293abe6d8beb769e123442fdf7e9bfa22489e3cc","tid":1715390,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:38:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登冷氣軍師 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你哋已經唔使上前線搏命，係咪連呢啲都做唔到？</span><br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLafS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=abc97cb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLafS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=23d6317b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F119434944634